	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well... there are several posts on this forum and as well as on other web sites concerning the pet-xp question.<br>So this what they say:<br>Pets take 50% of the xp if they do more damage than the mage (common from lvls 4 to 8... but unlikely after that since you get some good dd spells at lvl 8)<br><br>Pets take NO xp if the mage does more damage than the pet<br><br>AND pets don't take any xp in groups<br><br>Hope this helps a bit ;)&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Martinet Morgentau,<br>Gretelchen </td></tr>
