	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok... this is how i did it it.<br>From lvls 4 to 12 i used WATER it has a lot of HP (not as much as earth but still more than any other pet) a good deal of agi (it's not getting hit as hard as earth) a awesome hp regen rate and a decent dd... so it does more dmg than earth (some people think earth hits harder cause it has more strenght... that's not true) the only downside is that it doesn't root... but since you won't do that massive dmg with your dds at these lvls it is pretty unlikely that you will overagro the mob.<br><br>At 16th i got that fine shock of flame spell... it hits for 91dmg and will go up to 97.... and mobs don't like that too much... so&nbsp;&nbsp;i used earth to keep them of me.<br><br>Ok and at 20th i realized that the only pet that my guild sells is air.... so i used it... and loved it :)) even when i bought earth in the oot i still used air since it keeps the mob of u with its stun spell and doesn't get hit that often and that hard as earth meaning it will have the same percentge of its hp left at the end of the fight but won't take as much time to regen as earth does.<br>&nbsp;<br>Martinet Morgentau,<br>Gretelchen </td></tr>
